{"tid":1015974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[又贏】智能手機輻射排行榜出爐，最強輻射就是.....","createTime":"2019-02-10T13:21:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T14:54:51.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"acd6801029f9784668ed39ac2d426cd40a6073bd","tid":1015974,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T13:21:36.000Z","msg":"日前德國聯邦輻射防護辦公室發佈 2 份關於輻射的測試結果榜單，1 份是高輻射產品排名，而另 1 份則是低輻射產品排名，而檢測標準為瓦/千克。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/423423324332.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F423423324332.jpg&h=3bfbd81b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在高輻射產品排名中，以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">小米 A1 </span>(第 1 部採用原生 Android 系統的智能電話) 最高 1.75 瓦/千克，之後 3 位<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">都是小米及 OnePlus 的產品</span>，頭 10 名中小米及 OnePlus 各佔 3 部，可以說不少，但當中 Samsung 的產品卻 1 部也沒有。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/234233332.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F234233332.jpg&h=34a46e10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而最低輻射產品，第 1 位是 Galaxy Note 8 &ndash; 0.17 瓦/千克！而且頭 10 名中 Samsung 有多逹 5 部。。。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2019/02/10/the-phones-emitting-the-most-radiation/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2019%2F02%2F10%2Fthe-phones-emitting-the-most-radiation%2F&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=e1d5d003\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2019/02/10/the-phones-emitting-the-most-radiation/</a>"},{"pid":"af00e14463a7a70ef6182b34bd289c525fbd7adb","tid":1015974,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T13:23:37.000Z","msg":"咁驚咪寫信囉"},{"pid":"ac14833255099e5236275c336148dfec064dcdb9","tid":1015974,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T13:24:06.000Z","msg":"